{"about_the_game":"Originally released in 1983 for the ZX Spectrum, this unique and bizarre game saw players fight a new and sinister force: a form of mouth bacteria called Dentorium Kamikazium (DK). Now, relive those days in this remastered emulated version.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2>Move your toothbrush in front of the Imagico toothpaste tube to receive a squirt of toothpaste (containing the only known substance that can combat the DKs: the recently developed chemical compound DKX 11). Move to a tooth and scrub to clean it and repel the DKs, which are unrelenting in their attacks!<br><br><br>This enhanced version introduces a number of modern features to this retro classic, including:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Saving/loading the game at any point<br></li><li> Support for most modern game controllers<br></li><li> Full control remapping<br></li><li> Image scaling and smoothing options</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1660744158","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094290/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1660744158","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094290/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1660744158","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2094290/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1660744158","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"Originally released in 1983 for the ZX Spectrum, this unique and bizarre game saw players fight a new and sinister force: a form of mouth bacteria called Dentorium Kamikazium (DK). Now, relive those days in this remastered emulated version.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Gameplay</h2>Move your too